        <item>
            <title>智能門鎖爆炸炸爛半間屋，中國市監局：逾 3 成電子鎖不合格</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/10/smart-lock-explosion/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=smart-lock-explosion</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/10/smart-lock-explosion/wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 06:00:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居無線]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子門鎖]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290693</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="break-words">日前 Threads 網友 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@jjwilliamjj/post/DFvHE6nS8d3">@jjwilliamjj</a> 發文分享指有電子鎖爆炸，並炸毀了近半個單位。jjwilliamjj 分享的影片可見，電子鎖爆炸至變型，推開門更發現大半個單位傢俬被爆炸波及炸爛，幸而當時無人受傷。</p><blockquote id="ig-tp-DFvHE6nS8d3" class="text-post-media" style="background: #FFF; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 540px; margin: 1px; min-width: 270px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px); border: 1px solid #00000026;" data-text-post-permalink="https://www.threads.net/@jjwilliamjj/post/DFvHE6nS8d3" data-text-post-version="0"><div style="padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;"><div style="display: block; height: 32px; width: 32px; padding-bottom: 20px;"></div><div style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; color: #000000; font-weight: 600;">在 Threads 查看</div></div></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.threads.net/embed.js"></script></p><p>事故發生於中國貴州住宅區，初步顯示起火點疑為電子門鎖，該部位損毀尤其嚴重。事件曝光後，社會輿論紛紛聚焦電子門鎖安全性，特別是其內部鋰電池是否易於短路並引發火災。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290694" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210125558-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210125558-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210125558.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@jjwilliamjj/post/DFvHE6nS8d3">jjwilliamjj@X</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290695" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210125923-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210125923-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210125923.jpg 1070w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@jjwilliamjj/post/DFvHE6nS8d3">jjwilliamjj@X</a></p><p>下面有網民分享成龍經典迷因「中國的會爆炸」，另外亦有人指質疑單單一個電子鎖為何可以引起如此大的爆炸。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210_1_05_19-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210_1_05_19-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210_1_05_19.jpg 902w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@jjwilliamjj/post/DFvHE6nS8d3">jjwilliamjj@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210_1_04_37-694x118.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="118" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210_1_04_37-694x118.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250210_1_04_37.jpg 903w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@jjwilliamjj/post/DFvHE6nS8d3">jjwilliamjj@X</a></p><p>《HK01》引述中國市場監管總局關於電子門鎖抽查結果顯示，有逾 34% 樣本不及格，42 件個抽查樣本當中有 23 個未能通過阻燃測試。中國市場監管總局建議民眾選購電子鎖時需購買具有中國 3C 認證款式，另外亦需要選購有緊急快速開門功能的電子門鎖，必要時能夠越過電子程序，使用機械結構開鎖直接逃生。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@jjwilliamjj/post/DFvHE6nS8d3">jjwilliamjj@X</a>、<a href="https://www.threads.net/@jjwilliamjj/post/DFvHE6nS8d3">ilifepost</a>、<a href="https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/1101045/%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%96%80%E9%8E%96%E9%8B%B0%E9%9B%BB%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%8B%E7%9B%A1%E6%AF%80-threads%E8%84%86%E5%8F%8B-%E6%92%9E%E9%8C%AF%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E6%9C%83%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E6%AF%80%E6%BB%85?#google_vignette">HK01</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/10/smart-lock-explosion/wireless-home/">智能門鎖爆炸炸爛半間屋，中國市監局：逾 3 成電子鎖不合格</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
