        <item>
            <title>傳 Nothing 將推頭戴式耳機，支援消噪功能 + 全透明 LED 燈帶設計</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/10/nothing-rumors-head1-in-development/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nothing-rumors-head1-in-development</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/10/nothing-rumors-head1-in-development/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 03:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Head (1)]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nothing]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290672</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>提起 Nothing 這個品牌，早前就已傳出多項有關他們最新智能手機的消息，但今次的消息就有點不同，根據消息指出，Nothing 似乎有意在今年推出旗下首款頭戴式耳機 Head (1)。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_003-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_003-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_003.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_002-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_002-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_004-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_004-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_004.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>其實 Nothing 推出耳機也不是甚麼新鮮事，在他們旗下現時已有多款真無線藍牙耳機，包括：Ear、Ear (a)、CMF Buds、Ear Stick、Ear (open) 等，不過如果真的推出 Head (1)，就真的是旗下首款頭戴式耳機款式。據消息指，這款開發代號名為 B170 的耳機，將會具備十分不錯的消噪功能，而且支援 5W 充電格式，而早在大約年半前，Nothing 的 CEO 裴宇就已在 X 分享過由支持者設計的 Head (1) 渲染圖，所以今日流出他們有意推出旗下首款頭戴式耳機，絕非空穴來風。不過有關這款耳機就暫時未有進一步消息，是否真的採用與手機及其他耳機相同的透明式 + LED 燈帶設計，以及各項規格依然是個謎。希望今年稍後時份我們可以獲得更多進一步消息，之後再為各位 unwire.hk 讀者揭曉吧。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.smartprix.com/bytes/nothing-might-launch-wireless-headphones-later-this-year/">smartprix</a>、<a href="https://x.com/getpeid/status/1580001210450731008">X</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
